{"tid":911621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鴨脷洲大橋男子跳橋 倒20米下地面斃命","createTime":"2018-11-22T04:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T05:07:34.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"209141b3486280cab12e23565b5d89197b915738","tid":911621,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"早上9時半，一名女子(34歲)報案，指其男友在香港仔鴨脷洲大橋跳橋自殺，跌落約20米下地面。救援人員到場，經檢驗證實男事主當場身亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查得悉，死者姓盧30歲。現場檢獲遺書，初步調查事件沒有可疑，死者有感情問題困擾。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPM8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=831b0bdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181122/58943283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943283&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPM8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ab141676\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943283&h=0dcb70df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181122/58943283</a>"},{"pid":"288f92046b2dcf4622800c810513bdb9c2d663d4","tid":911621,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:59:16.000Z","msg":"條女老佢咁多所以跳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條女好可疑"},{"pid":"be7514dc85863cc1383c366f0e589c2404730068","tid":911621,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"8－90後買唔起樓，唔死冇用啦。"},{"pid":"ae3316e8d83f20890b5b06e2e11661